ime":"2019-07-03T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"所以幾時都話連登仔愛國愛黨<br />\n大佬.毛主席既說話都夠膽唔敢<br />\n罰你去毛語錄一千次<br />\n<br />\n點似得香港討論區.親子王國<br />\n反中亂港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55d482bbfc5f308e1f970060f046d9c2ecb67b4","tid":1282570,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b61604682ce982e413c8a706b1014f547a7db63","tid":1282570,"uid":46966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"毛主席真係革命偉人<br />\n咁多年D語錄都中哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"無錯.當五毛一出現時<br />\n我地比起五毛更加愛黨<br />\n大佬.你連毛澤東既經典名詞都唔9識<br />\n學乜人做五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bbf8fb4266540a470e5144c06c7ed6bf0f5352","tid":1282570,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:24:55.000Z","msg":"「一個不是人民選舉出來的政府，有甚麼臉面代表這個國家？愛這樣的國家，就是對祖國的背叛。」這是誰說的呢？這是中共建政前《解放日報》在1944年6月13日刊登的毛澤東的話，原話摘自《毛澤東答中外記者團》，回應當時國民黨關於「全國人民團結一致，愛國御敵」的號召時說出的。毛澤東當時還指出：「現在談愛國？那是愛誰的國？蔣介石的國吧。。。少數人的國，由他們少數人去愛吧。」<br />\n<br />\n下次記住識得點回啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e52973f2d8e9a2ea0d67575eb267bd366f05eb","tid":1282570,"uid":226233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"支持"}]}